data.description: This charming home offers an abundance of potential, with its spacious layout on almost a quarter of an acre features a giant drive way enough for 5 vehicles plus a 2 car garage. It has a concrete U shape slab surrounding the entire property. Roof and the Hvac system were replaced 2 years ago. This Home showcases a large backyard perfect for gardening enthusiasts, and its prime location in a family-friendly neighborhood makes it an ideal opportunity for those with a vision for renovation and a desire to create their dream home.
